<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Verified - Welcome Back!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #28a745; /* Green button color */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Congratulations, <%= name %>!</h1>
        <p>Your account has been successfully verified. You are now ready to create and share your courses on Learning Platform. We’re thrilled to have you as part of our educator community!</p>
        <p>To get started, click the button below to create your first course:</p>
        <a href="<%= Link %>" class="button">Create Your Course</a>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Learning Platform Team</p>
            <p>If you did not request this verification, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
